suggest.ext-sodium: Sodium is required for OKP key creation, EdDSA signature algorithm and ECDH-ES key encryption with OKP keys
suggest.bjeavons/zxcvbn-php: Adds key quality check for oct keys.
suggest.symfony/serializer: Use the Symfony serializer to serialize/unserialize JWS and JWE tokens.
suggest.symfony/var-dumper: Used to show data on the debug toolbar.
